section.section:
Except as provided in paragraphs (2) through (5) of this subsection, all reports and all information collected in connection with a report from a health care provider, the subject of the report, or other individuals who might be affected by the condition or disease in the report are:
Confidential;
Not medical records under Title 4, Subtitle 3 of this article;
Not open to public inspection; and
Not discoverable or admissible in evidence in any civil or criminal matter except in accordance with a court order sealing the court record.
